              <description>A club that is always striving for the best and encourages our players to shoot for the stars!</description>
              <circle><a href="../Portfolio/portfolio.html"><i class="fa-solid fa-play"></i></a></circle>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="pictureArea"><section class="picture"><img src="images/ALL_Soccer_110122.jpg" alt="Picture Error"></section></section>
        <section class="main">
            <maintext>
                At Dynamite FC, we believe in the power of passion, teamwork, and explosive talent. We're more than just a football club; we're a community where players grow, thrive, and ignite their full potential. Whether you're an aspiring star or a seasoned player looking for a new challenge, Dynamite FC is the perfect place to elevate your game. Join us on the pitch, and let’s create something extraordinary together. Are you ready to be a part of the explosion? Apply now and bring your dynamite spirit to the field!
            </maintext>
            <a href="../About/about.html"><button> READ MORE</button></a>
        </section>
